OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1780992973
OL,3,CTeenager who died at lake named as
OL,4,Cinquest opens into his death
OL,6,FA teenager who died after going
OL,7,Fmissing at a lake in Hampshire has
OL,8,Fbeen named as 14-year-old Samuel
OL,9,FMurphy.
OL,11,FSamuel, who was from Camberley, had
OL,12,Fbeen swimming at Hawley Lake near
OL,13,FBlackwater during the heatwave last
OL,14,Fmonth.
OL,16,FAn inquest opened at Winchester
OL,17,FCoroner's Court on Monday, with
OL,18,Fcoronor Rosamund Rhodes-Kemp offering
OL,19,Fher condolences to Samuel's family.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
