PN,41602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1780992973
OL,3,CTeenager who died at lake named as
OL,4,Cinquest opens into his death
OL,6,FThe inquest heard that on 26 May, the
OL,7,F14-year-old went to Hawley Lake with
OL,8,Ffriends during half term, but when
OL,9,Fthey lost sight of him they contacted
OL,10,Fthe emergency services.
OL,12,FEmergency services arrived at the
OL,13,FMinistry of Defence site and then
OL,14,Freturned the following day when they
OL,15,Fdiscovered Samuel's body.
OL,17,FThe coroner has now asked for
OL,18,Fstatements from witnesses, the MoD and
OL,19,FSamuel's family before the full
OL,20,Finquest takes place in July 2027.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
