FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1780992973
OL,3,CTeenager who died at lake named as
OL,4,Cinquest opens into his death
OL,6,FMrs Rhodes-Kemp raised her concerns
OL,7,Fabout the number of deaths in lakes
OL,8,Frecently.
OL,10,FAt the opening of the inquest, she
OL,11,Fsaid that she is the chair of a parish
OL,12,Fcouncil where more than 100 young
OL,13,Fpeople go swimming, and that she wants
OL,14,Fto raise awareness about the dangers.
OL,16,FAt least 17 people are reported to
OL,17,Fhave died after getting into trouble
OL,18,Fin open water during the UK heatwave.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
