PN,41604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1780992973
OL,3,CTeenager who died at lake named as
OL,4,Cinquest opens into his death
OL,6,FThis includes Baltazar L'Qui, 14, near
OL,7,FDonnington Bridge and an unnamed boy
OL,8,Fin Swanscombe, Kent.
OL,10,FThe Royal Life Saving Society (RLSS)
OL,11,Fissued a warning following the deaths,
OL,12,Fsaying it sees a "heightened risk of
OL,13,Fdrowning when air temperatures are
OL,14,Fhigher".
OL,16,FThis all comes as temperatures dropped
OL,17,Ftowards the average for the time of
OL,18,Fyear following the heatwave.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
